\c 4
\s Erifazi anoyeudzira Jobho kuti atende Mwari agorwirwa hake
\p
\v 1 Ipapo Erifazi muTemani akapi- ndura, akati,
\p
\v 2 "Kana munhu akaidza kutaurirana newe, iwe uchava
\s neshungu here?
\s Asi ndiani angazvidzora,
\s akasataura hake?
\p
\v 3 Tarira, iwe wakadzidzisa vazhinji, Iwe wakasimbisa maoko akashaiwa simba.
\p
\v 4 Mashoko ako akatsigira akanga achivavarira kuwa,
\s Iwe wakasimbisa mabvi akanga achigweda-gweda.
\p
\v 5 Asi zvino zvasvika kwauri, iwe woshaiwa simba;
\p Zvakubata, zvino wotambudzika.
\v 6 Ko kutya kwako Mwari harizi simba rako here?
\s Kururama kwenzira dzako haizi tariro yako here?
\p
\v 7 Rangarira hako, ndianiko asine mhaka akatongoparara?
\s Kana vakarurama vakatongoparadzwa papi?
\p
\v 8 Sezvandakaona ini, vanhu,
\s vanorimira zvakaipa,
\s Navanodyara zvakashata, ndivo vanokohwawo izvozvo.
\p
\v 9 Vanoparadzwa nomweya waMwari,
\s Vanopedzwa nokufema kwokutsamwa kwake.
\p
\v 10 Kunduruma kweshumba nezwi reshumba inehasha,
\s Nameno evana veshumba anoparadzwa.
\p
\v 11 Shumba, yakwegura, inofa nokushaiwa zvingabata;
\s Navana veshumbakadzi vanoparadzirwa.
\p
\v 12 Zvino ndakaziviswa shoko rakavanda;
\s Nzeve yangu yakanzwa zeve-zeve raro.
\p
\v 13 Pandangariro dzinobva pane zvinoonekwa usiku,
\s Kana vanhu vabatwa nehope huru;
\p
\v 14 Kutya nokubvunda kwakandiwira, Kwakabvundisa mapfupa angu ose.
\p
\v 15 Ipapo mweya wakapfuura pamberi pechiso changu;
\s Mvere dzenyama yangu dzikasimuka.
\p
\v 16 Wakamira, asi ndakanga
\s ndisingagoni kuona kuti akadini;
\s Mufananidzo wangu wakanga uri
\s pamberi pameso angu;
\s Kunyarara kukavapo, ndikanzwa izwi richiti,
\p
\v 17 â€˜Ko munhu, anofa, angakunda Mwari pakururama here?
\s Ko munhu angakunda Muiti wake pakunaka here?
\p
\v 18 Tarirai, haatendi varanda vake; Vatumwa vake anovapa mhaka achiti mapenzi;
\p
\v 19 Ndoda vanogara mudzimba dzevhu,
\s Nheyo dzadzo dzakateyiwa paguruva,
\s Dzinopwanyiwa sezvivhundudzi.
\p
\v 20 Vanoparadzwa pakati pamagwanani namadekwana;
\s Vanoparara nokusingaperi, pasina munhu ane hanya nazvo.
\p
\v 21 Ko bote retente ravo harina kuvhomorwa pamwechete navo here? Vanofa vasina uchenjeri.' "
